\ip Jut r…ômwhen ia Jemes, in pi…ôvi Iesu. In r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô…°kiari ia nahat…ôn eiku…ô me s…ôm…ôme Pita ram…ô…°kiari ia nir…ôha ia n…ôkuku…ô s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ro k…ôru ir…ô. Jut in mwi r…®ni m…ô nakalasia me tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôsiari kamo nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha h…ôkoui irapw ir…ôha ia suatuk atukwatukw. Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha ham…ôni m…ô Iesu r…®pko mh…ô in T…®ni Kumwes…ôn. Ir…ôha kamh…ôiri pen n…ôrmama ia noien …ôr…ôha. Jut r…®ni m…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi nahat…ôn eiku…ô me mouraha ir…ôha. R…ômwhen in r…®n…ôrpw…®n raka noien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ôi na…°elo …ôr…ôha me m…®ne n…ôrmama …ôr…ôha me ia n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi Oltestamen.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rakupw…ôn  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Mat 13:55\x*Iou Jut. Iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamo tukwini nari m Iesu Kristo. Piak n…ô Jemes. Iakamrai n…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha n…ôrmama me i Tata Kumwes…ôn r…®nokeikei k…®miaha, m…ôkwein ia k…®miaha. Iesu Kristo in ram…ôtui amasan tukumiaha.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 2Tes 1:2\x*Pw…ôh Kumwes…ôn tr…ôriari pehe napiien, n…ôm…ôrinuien, m…®ne nokeikeiien m k…®miaha. Pw…ôh ir…ôhar harasori mwi tukumiaha.   
\s1 N…ôkur …ôr…ôha me m…®ne n…ôrpw…®nien s…ô Kumwes…ôn tro m…®nraha  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1Tim 1:18\x*Piak keikei me. Fwe kupw…ôn iakokeikei p…®k m…ô takrai n…ôkuku…ô i m k…®miaha, m…ô…°kiari ia suatuk s…ôk…®taha p…ôri Kumwes…ôn rauvehim…®ru k…®taha ir…ô. M…ôt…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni iakre…°i m…ô takam…ôkeikei m…®rai n…ô…°kiariien i, m…®ni pehe tukumiaha m…ô tiham…ôkeikei mhousari mh…ôkwt…ômhiri …ôknek…®n n…ô…°kiariien i k…®taha samahat…ôt…ô ir…ô. In i n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien s…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôuvei pen m n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô tr…®pkuvei pen mh…ô mwi ia n…ôp…®n riti mwi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Kal 2:4, 2Tes 2:1\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrmama nepw…®n h…ôuv…ôuvehe afafa raka ia nous…ôs…®mw…®nien s…ôk…®miaha. Ir…ôha n…ôkur …ôr…ôha me. Kamh…ôkoui namasanien i Kumwes…ôn rauvehim…®ru k…®taha ir…ô ruvehe mo nari riti s…ô ram…ôseni ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn noien n…ôfe n…ô…°h…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien …ôr…ôha s…ôv…ônraha rokeikei. Ir…ôha kamh…ôuvsini t…ôkutanraha m Iesu Kristo, m…ôt…ô in …ôpa n…ôha I…ôm…ô asori m…®ne I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha. Kuv…ôrai pen raka tui ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan n…ôfe n…ôrpw…®nien Kumwes…ôn truvei pen m…®nraha.   
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 2Tes 1:12, 1Kor 10:5\x*Iaku…ô tako rer…®miaha r…®rhi nari m nari me nepw…®n s…ôm…ôme hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka. Fwe tui I…ôr…®m…ônu r…®m…ôuvehim…®ru n…ôkur Isrel, miri raka ir…ôha ia t…ôn…ô Ijip, m…ôt…ô kurir…ô rousi …ôpune ir…ôha n…ôha s…ôm…ôme h…ôpk…®ni mh…ô n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt 2Tes 2:4,9\x*N…ôn…ô rer…®miaha tr…®rhi ro na…°elo me n…ôha fwe kupw…ôn s…ôm…ôme h…ôpk…ôkwt…ômhiri mh…ô nasoriien s…ô kauvei pen m…®nraha, m…ôt…ô haraka ir…ô, mh…ôpw…ôh kwopun atukwatukw s…ôv…ônraha. Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôrihi ir…ôha ia jen me s…ôm…ôme tuh…ôpkiw…ôn mh…ô, m…ômri pen ir…ôha fwe inh…ôr…®pw ia kwopun r…®pit…ôv ik…®n. Tuhamar…ô ik…®n meste n…ôp…®n asori s…ô Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha ir…ô.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Jen 19:1-25, 2Tes 2:6,10\x*N…ôn…ô tih…ôpw…ôh nenouenouien taon mi n…ôha Sotom m…®ne Komora m…®ne rukw…ônu me ipaka fwe kupw…ôn. Napw rahi pam n…ôrmama me ik…®n t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôrman m…®ne n…®pran kamh…ôiri …ôpnapen ir…ôha me, n…ôrman me kamh…ôiri atukw a ir…ôha me. N…ôrmama me n…ôha h…ômwhen ia nahat…ôn penien riti s…ô ramahat…ôn pen n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha ia napw s…ô rau…ôk rer…®n.   
\p
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt 2Tes 2:10\x*Ia noien me n…ôha r…ômwhen a mwi n…ôrmama me i iakam…ô…°kiari ia nir…ôha kamh…ôkurir…ô n…ôm…ôkr…ôhaien me s…ôv…ônraha, mamho noien …ômkem…®k ia n…®pwranraha, mamh…ôni m…ô I…ôr…®m…ônu in r…®pkasori mh…ô ia nir…ôha, n…ôn…ô mamh…ôni …ôr…ôha mwi na…°elo me fwe ia neiai.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Dan 10:13,21, Dan 12:1, 2Tes 2:11, Rev 12:7, Sek 3:2\x*M…ôt…ô Mikael i, a…°elo s…ô rasori ia na…°elo me pam, in r…®pko mh…ô iam…®nhi. Fwe kupw…ôn, n…ôp…®n krou…ôvis…ô irau Setan m…ô sin truvehi n…®pwrai Moses m…®n…®mwi, in r…®pkuvehi ut…ô mh…ô in m…®ni n…ô…°kiariien …ôr…ôha riti mu…ôsi Setan i. M…ôt…ô in r…®ni a m…ô, ‚ÄúPw…ôh I…ôr…®m…ônu tr…®nise ik.‚Äù  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2Tes 2:12\x*M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama me i, tr…®ni m…®nu…ô h…ôreirei n…®pwrai nari riti, tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôni …ôr…ôha. Ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia n…ôri …ôprm…®n me s…ôv…ônraha n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien riw…ôn. Hamo a n…ôfe narimnari me rer…®nraha rokeikei, n…ôn…ô noien n…ôha ramouraha a ir…ôha.   
