\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1Jon 3:12, 2Tes 2:15, Nam 16:1-35\x*Aueh, tr…ôr…ôha anan t…® nir…ôha! Ir…ôha kamhesi pen suatuk n…ô Ken\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Jen 4:3-8\x* r…®nesi pen. Ir…ôha hokeikei p…®k mane mamh…ômwei ia n…ôr…ôhaien n…ôha Palam\x - \xo 1:11 \xt Nam 31:16\x* r…®no. Ir…ôha atukw a kamhouraha ir…ôha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô kamh…ôrer mamh…ôni …ôr…ôha Kumwes…ôn r…ômwhen ia Kora r…®no.   
