\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Jen 5:21-24, Dut 33:2, Mat 25:31\x*Inok, i…ôrmama s…ô ro sefen ruku pen ia kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Atam, r…®ni irapw n…ô…°kiariien s…ô Kumwes…ôn ruvei pen min, mukupw…ôn m…ô…°kiari ia n…ôrmama me i, m…®ni m…ô,  
