\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 2Pit 2:10,18\x*N…ôrmama me i kamho n…ô…°kiariien me t…® n…®ni …ôr…ôhaien nari. Ko ir…ôha h…ôpkafafa mh…ô. Kamhesi pen n…ôfe noien …ôr…ôha n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha rokeikei. Kamh…ôfi…ôut…ô atukw a ia nir…ôha me. Kamh…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni n…ôrmama, m…ôt…ô ho a m…ô n…ôrmama tuhasitu ia nir…ôha.   
\s1 Rer…®miaha tramrhi n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi aposol me  
