\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt 2Tes 3:2\x*M…ôt…ô piak keikei me, rer…®miaha tram…ôkeikei m…®rhi n…ôfe aposol me s…ôv…ôi Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha h…ôuv…ôni raka fwe kupw…ôn m…ô trier irapw.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt 2Tes 3:3\x*H…ôm…ôni pehe tukumiaha i m…ô, ‚ÄúTramev…ôn ipaka t…® n…ôp…®n sampam n…ôrmama nepw…®n tuh…ôuvehe. Ir…ôha tuhar…®s ia k…®miaha, mamhesi pen n…ôfe noien …ôr…ôha n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha rokeikei, mamho narimnari me h…ôpw…ôh n…ômwhenien ia n…ômri Kumwes…ôn.‚Äù  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt 1Kor 2:14\x*N…ôrmama me i tuh…ôvis…ô mheitehi kusen s…ôk…®miaha. Ir…ôha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ôi t…®pr…ôn…ô i. N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan riw…ôn ia nir…ôha.   
