\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Kol 2:7, 1Tes 5:11\x*M…ôt…ô piak keikei me, k…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôrpwi …ôknek…®n k…®miaha me, mho nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha r…®skai. Nahat…ôt…ôien n…ôha ruku pen t…® Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô ro ikinan i. N…ôp…®n me tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôfwaki ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan,  
