\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Amos 4:11, Sek 3:2, Rev 3:4\x*N…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho noien …ôr…ôha me, tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôuvehi raka ir…ôha ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha. Tih…ôuvehim…®ru ir…ôha pw…ôh h…ôpw…ôh nev…ônien fwe ia napw. N…ôrmama nepw…®n mwi tiham…ôkeikei mhapi ir…ôha, mhehek…®r mwi ir…ôha. N…ôri au…ôr a m…ô t…®nari s…ôv…ônraha, m…ôt…ô tih…ôhek…®r i, mh…ôpw…ôh n…®rapiien, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô r…ômkem…®k ia n…ôr…ôhaien s…ôv…ônraha.   
