\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Fil 1:10, 2Tes 3:14\x*Kumwes…ôn in …ôpa tr…ôkwt…ômhiri k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôpw…ôh n…®mweiien. In …ôpa tro hi…ôuv…ôn mh…ôrer ia n…ônimen ia kwopun s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ram…ôhiapw, k…®miaha tihatukwatukw pam, mamha…°ien asori.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Rom 16:27, 2Tes 3:18\x*Kumwes…ôn i s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha ia n…ô…°hi Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha in …ôpa Kumwes…ôn. Pw…ôh n…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien, m…®ne n…ôr…®m…ônuien, m…®ne n…®skaiien, m…®ne nasoriien h…ôuv…ôn …ôpa tukwe fwe tui n…ôp…®n t…®pr…ôn…ô ramiw…ôn ihi, ipwet m…®ne, mamev…ôn meste nuk nuk me. Ou…ôh, pw…ôh ro iam…®nhi.   